you by surprise - and that's what this video

00:00:26.270 --> 00:00:27.270
is all about.

00:00:27.270 --> 00:00:30.820
Here's our latest edition of twenty rapid
fire behind the scenes movie facts...

00:00:30.820 --> 00:00:33.260
Thor: Ragnorok
Taika Waititi will direct Thor: Ragnarok,

00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:36.330
which will make the movie the first Marvel
Studios franchise to have three different

00:00:36.330 --> 00:00:37.710
directors for each film.

00:00:37.710 --> 00:00:41.460
Kenneth Branagh directed Thor and Alan Taylor
directed Thor: The Dark World.

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:43.530
Deadpool
The full body make up that Ryan Reynolds had

00:00:43.530 --> 00:00:46.329
to wear as Deadpool took eight hours to apply.

00:00:46.329 --> 00:00:50.960
Once it was applied, he wasn't allowed to
either sit or lie down.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:54.260
The Angry Birds Movie
The Angry Birds Movie is the most costly movie

00:00:54.260 --> 00:00:55.410
to ever come out of Final.

00:00:55.410 --> 00:00:59.469
It had a production budget of $80 million,
and there was an additional $100 million spent

00:00:59.469 --> 00:01:00.469
on marketing.

00:01:00.469 --> 00:01:03.269
Alien: Covenant
The 2007 sequel to Prometheus was originally

00:01:03.269 --> 00:01:08.460
going to be called Alien: Paradise Lost, but
the title was changed to Alien: Covenant.

00:01:08.460 --> 00:01:12.430
The Conjuring 2
Director James Wan was offered a "life altering"

00:01:12.430 --> 00:01:16.050
amount of money to direct 2017's Fast 8, but
he turned the opportunity down to direct The

00:01:16.050 --> 00:01:17.070
Conjuring 2.

00:01:17.070 --> 00:01:20.500
He said he felt "rejuvenated to tell a scary
story one more time", having previously directed

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:21.500
the first Conjuring movie and two of the Insidious
installments.

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:25.650
Rogue One: A Star Wars Story
The female lead role of Jyn Erso in Rogue

00:01:25.650 --> 00:01:29.960
One: A Star Wars Story, which ultimately went
to Felicity Jones, was auditioned for by a

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:32.920
pair of actress sisters in Kate and Rooney
Mara.

00:01:32.920 --> 00:01:36.530
Wonder Woman
Zack Snyder - of Batman v Superman directorial

00:01:36.530 --> 00:01:40.970
fame - will cameo in the first Wonder Woman
solo movie as a World War I soldier.

00:01:40.970 --> 00:01:43.410
He will also be credited as a producer on
the movie.

00:01:43.410 --> 00:01:45.260
The Hateful Eight
2015's brilliant The Hateful Eight was originally

00:01:45.260 --> 00:01:47.580
planned to be much longer than the final version.

00:01:47.580 --> 00:01:52.230
Early test screenings had a runtime of over
three hours and actually included an intermission.

00:01:52.230 --> 00:01:55.530
Creed
Sylvester Stallone is a big fan of English

00:01:55.530 --> 00:01:57.100
Premier League soccer team, Everton.

00:01:57.100 --> 00:02:01.820
As a result, some of the crowd scenes in Creed
were filmed at the Everton versus WBA game

00:02:01.820 --> 00:02:03.310
on a cold Monday night in England.

00:02:03.310 --> 00:02:05.310
10 Cloverfield Lane
Throughout the entirety of the filming of

00:02:05.310 --> 00:02:08.929
10 Cloverfield Lane, the movie's cast weren't
told the title of the movie.

00:02:08.929 --> 00:02:11.920
The idea was (obviously) to keep the whole
thing as secret as possible.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:14.510
Spider-Man: Homecoming
Donald Glover has recently been confirmed

00:02:14.510 --> 00:02:16.530
to appear in Spider-Man: Homecoming, which
is very exciting.

00:02:16.530 --> 00:02:20.880
He's the second Community actor to star in
a Spider-Man movie, as Joel McHale had a cameo

00:02:20.880 --> 00:02:22.500
in Spider-Man 2.

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:24.840
Krampus
2015's Krampus was originally meant to be

00:02:24.840 --> 00:02:29.379
released on the 25th of November, but it was
delayed until the 4th of December to coincide

00:02:29.379 --> 00:02:33.930
with the Krampusnacht - a traditional Austrian
festival held on the 5th of December to celebrate

00:02:33.930 --> 00:02:36.180
the Krampus coming to punish naughty children.

00:02:36.180 --> 00:02:39.170
Sausage Party
When Seth Rogen and Evan Goldberg's hilarious-looking

00:02:39.170 --> 00:02:43.769
Sausage Party is released in August of 2016,
it will become the first American R-rated

00:02:43.769 --> 00:02:49.129
computer animated film since Aqua Teen Hunger
Force Colon Movie Film for Theaters in 2007.

00:02:49.129 --> 00:02:52.420
Ant-Man
Paul Rudd was the unexpected star of 2015's

00:02:52.420 --> 00:02:56.249
Ant-Man when he portrayed the titular Scott
Lang.

00:02:56.249 --> 00:02:59.629
When he told his nine-year-old daughter that
he was going to be Ant-Man, she said, "Wow,

00:02:59.629 --> 00:03:02.470
I can't wait to see how stupid that'll be."

00:03:02.470 --> 00:03:07.000
Dirty Grandpa
Dirty Grandpa's theatrical poster sees Robert

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.450
De Niro lifting Zac Efron onto his back.

00:03:09.450 --> 00:03:13.760
Whilst promoting the movie on Instagram, Efron
himself confirmed that De Niro did this without

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:15.189
any help or prompting.

00:03:15.189 --> 00:03:17.680
Spectre
Spectre was the first Bond film not to feature

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:20.499
the iconic trumpet playing of Derek Watkins.

00:03:20.499 --> 00:03:25.849
Ever since 1962's Dr. No, Watkins had featured
on the soundtrack of every single Bond outing.

00:03:25.849 --> 00:03:28.469
However, he passed away shortly after the
release of Skyfall.

00:03:28.469 --> 00:03:31.170
The Secret Life of Pets
Althought they are all big stars with multiple

00:03:31.170 --> 00:03:34.930
movies to their names, The Secret Life of
Pets marks the feature animation debut of

00:03:34.930 --> 00:03:40.129
several of its key cast, including Louis CK,
Eric Stonestreet and Kevin Hart.

00:03:40.129 --> 00:03:42.829
Warcraft
With orcs being key members of the cast of

00:03:42.829 --> 00:03:46.719
Warcraft, an "Orcish" dialect was created
specifically for the movie.

00:03:46.719 --> 00:03:48.849
Suicide Squad
Suicide Squad's release date in 2016 will

00:03:48.849 --> 00:03:54.341
come exactly fifty years after the Joker first
appeared in live action, back in 1966 when

00:03:54.341 --> 00:03:57.760
Cesar Romero portrayed the character on both
the small and big screen.

00:03:57.760 --> 00:03:59.890
Suicide Squad
Will Smith shaved his head and spent time

00:03:59.890 --> 00:04:04.059
training with Navy SEALS and Army Rangers
in order to prepare for his role as Deadshot

00:04:04.059 --> 00:04:05.169
in Suicide Squad.

00:04:05.169 --> 00:04:10.430
He practiced firing a Glock 9mm handgun and
an AR-15 rifle, and was apparently a very

00:04:10.430 --> 00:04:11.450
quick learner.

